<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Sarbanes-Oxley_Act&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Similar laws in other countries">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Similar laws in other countries</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Bill_198" title="Bill 198">Bill 198</a> — Ontario, Canada, equivalent of Sarbanes-Oxley Act</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/J-SOX" title="J-SOX" class="mw-redirect">J-SOX</a> — Japanese equivalent of Sarbanes-Oxley Act</li>
<li><a href="http://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deutscher_Corporate_Governance_Kodex" class="extiw" title="de:Deutscher Corporate Governance Kodex">German Corporate Governance Code</a> (at the German Wikipedia)</li>
