<li><a href="/wiki/Financial_Security_Law_of_France" title="Financial Security Law of France">Financial Security Law of France</a> ("Loi sur la Sécurité Financière") — French equivalent of Sarbanes-Oxley Act</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=L262/2005&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="L262/2005 (page does not exist)">L262/2005</a> ("Disposizioni per la tutela del risparmio e la disciplina dei mercati finanziari") — Italian equivalent of Sarbanes-Oxley Act for financial services institutions</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/King_Report" title="King Report">King Report</a> — South African corporate governance code</li>
</ul>
